The idea was for the three SCPs to be interconnected, related to the same originating event, and presumably related to some originating group (though the latter is NOT supposed to be seen as a GoI, hence all the mystery and vague references). Basically, one single article containing all of these events would be bugfuck long and inordinately complex, given that the Foundation can obviously see that there is a connection between them but has absolutely no means of putting it together. Moreover, the most conspicuous shared thread is the amorphous blackness, and that's not meant to be a character so much as aside-effect.







